description:
RealSimpleEDU.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for "Chemistry"

  App offers quizzes and tutorials to help you learn Chemistry

  App is continuously updated based on your feedback.

  App offers tutorials and quizzes with search feature.


  Includes following tutorials:

  Basics of Chemistry,
  Atomic Theory,
  Basis of Quantum Mechanics,
  Orbital Filling,
  Quantum Numbers,
  Chemical Bonding I,
  Chemical Bonding II,
  Equations and Reactions,
  The Periodic Table,
  Periodic Trends,
  Periodic Table Properties I,
  Periodic Table Properties II,
  Solids and Liquids,
  Gas and Gas Laws,
  Solutions,
  Osmosis,
  Heat,
  Chemical Kinetics,
  Reaction Mechanisms,
  Hydrocarbons,
  Adding Atoms to Hydrocarbons,
  Carbon Based Molecules,
  Vitamins and Proteins,
  Organic Chemistry,
  Methods of Purification,
  Chromatography and Types,
  Stoichiometry,
  Biochemistry,
  Hormones,
  Classes of Biochemistry,
  Radioactivity,
  Electrochemistry.



  Includes following Quizzes:

  Quiz on Basics of Chemistry and Atomic Theory
  Quiz on Quantum Mechanics, Orbital Filling and Quantum Numbers
  Quiz on Chemical Bonding, Equations and Reactions
  Quiz on Periodic Table and its Properties
  Quiz on Solids, Liquids and Gases
  Quiz on Hydrocarbons and Carbon Based Molecules
  Quiz on Organic Chemistry, Chromatography and Stoichiometry
  Quiz on Biochemistry, Hormones and Electrochemistry



  Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.

  Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.

  Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
